(57, 'Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X', '36 Tháng', '18399000', 100, '9.jpg', '<p>Nh&acirc;n đồ họa: NVIDIA&reg; GeForce RTX&trade; 4070</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nh&acirc;n CUDA: 5888</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dung lượng bộ nhớ: 12GB GDDR6X</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nguồn khuyến nghị: 650W</p>\r\n', '<p>Đ&aacute;nh gi&aacute;: Card m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X (\" src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/14-04-2023/card-man-hinh-asus-tuf-rtx-4070-12g-gaming-mota1.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /><img alt=\"Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X (\" src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/14-04-2023/card-man-hinh-asus-tuf-rtx-4070-12g-gaming-mota2.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /><img alt=\"Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X (\" src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/14-04-2023/card-man-hinh-asus-tuf-rtx-4070-12g-gaming-mota3.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /><img alt=\"Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X (\" src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/14-04-2023/card-man-hinh-asus-tuf-rtx-4070-12g-gaming-mota4.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /><img alt=\"Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X (\" src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/14-04-2023/card-man-hinh-asus-tuf-rtx-4070-12g-gaming-mota5.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /><img alt=\"Card màn hình Asus TUF RTX 4070-12G-GAMING GDDR6X (\" src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/14-04-2023/card-man-hinh-asus-tuf-rtx-4070-12g-gaming-mota6.jpg\" style=\"width:100%\" /></p>\r\n', 1, 36, NULL),
